3... Nxe4 4. dxe5
{ Making it impossible for the knight to go back to the safe f6-square. We can put pressure on Black's knight.  After  4...Bc5  attacking the f2-pawn, a sharp battle starts in which we play  5.Bc4  counterattacking the f7-pawn! Study the Petrov chapter for all the details. }
