[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
[Round "?"]
[White "2. Scotch Gambit: Main Line with 4...Nf6 Tactics "]
[Black "Exercise 3: Scotch Gambit 4...Nf6"]
[Result "*"]
[FEN "r1bqk2r/pppp1ppp/2n2n2/4P3/1bBp4/5N2/PPP2PPP/RNBQK2R w KQkq - 0 6"]
[SetUp "1"]

{ How to cope with the check? } 6. c3
{ Now we are attacking both the knight and the bishop. } 6... dxc3 7. bxc3
{ We are attacking both the bishop and the knight and will win a piece. Please don't play the tempting  7.exf6  because it runs into the tactic with  7...cxb2+  and next, Black will capture your rook and promote. }
