4... d5 5. Nbd2
{ We attack the knight and try to make it move for the third time. } 5... Nc5
6. Be2 { Developing and getting ready to castle. } 6... Be7 7. O-O
{ White wants to continue by bringing the rook to the center with Re1. Also, we would like to play Nb3 and subsequently develop the dark-squared bishop. }
