{ We capture the bishop and allow Black to capture our rook, knowing that their knight will be misplaced in the corner. }
8... Nxh1
{ We shouldn't worry much about our rook in the corner. Black captures the rook, which was entirely out of play, and now the knight on h1 is in an awful position as well. }
