{ By far the most popular move at the 1600-level. This time we have a different trick. }
8. Qa4+
{ This check is deadly! We are unpinning the knight and attacking the king, knight, and bishop at the same time. White is winning a piece and the computer gives +7.   After  8...Qd7  we play  9.Bb5  pinning the queen, and if  9...Nc6  then  10.Qxg4  wins the bishop. Check how I won my online game in this variation. }
