f4
{ Defending against Qg3+ and preparing to get our knight on a beautiful outpost on e5. Also, we would like to trade Black's strong light-squared bishop with Bd3. White has a nice position. Check out who I lost this position with the Black pieces against FM Grieve in the model game. }
