{ 8...Bxg5  would benefit us since after  9.hxg5  our rook on h1 is activated. }
9. Nbd2
{ White has a lead in development and is ready to castle. Black is still struggling to develop the knight on g8.   After  9...Nh6  we play  10.Bxh6  and force Black to either move the rook and give up on the idea of a kingside castle or break the pawn structure.   After  9...Qb6  we play  10.O-O  when after  10...Qxb2  11.Bxe7  Nxe7  12.Rfb1!  we trap the queen! }
