{ Can you find the winning move? } 1. Qa4+
{ This check is deadly! We are unpinning the knight and attacking the king, knight, and bishop. White is winning a piece, and the computer gives  +7.  After  1...Qd7  we play  2.Bb5  pinning the queen and forcing Black to play  2...Nc6  and subsequently  3.Qxg4  wins the bishop. }
